# RPi - can publish scans, RSSI, heartbeats; read whitelist and ack checks; write ack results
user rpi
topic write hospital/medicine/scan/#
topic write hospital/medicine/rssi_only/#
topic write hospital/system/rpi_status/#
topic read hospital/system/whitelist
topic read hospital/medicine/ack_check/#
topic write hospital/medicine/ack_result/#
topic read hospital/medicine/command_ble/#
topic write hospital/medicine/command_ble_result/#

# M5Stick tags - emergency, ack, and command topics
user m5tag
topic write hospital/medicine/emergency/#
topic write hospital/medicine/ack/#
topic read hospital/medicine/command/#

# Coordinator (backend) - reads scans/emergencies/results, writes commands/checks/whitelist
user coordinator
topic read hospital/medicine/scan/#
topic read hospital/medicine/emergency/#
topic write hospital/medicine/rssi/#
topic write hospital/medicine/command/#
topic write hospital/system/coordinator_status
topic write hospital/system/whitelist
topic write hospital/medicine/ack_check/#
topic read hospital/medicine/ack_result/#
topic write hospital/medicine/command_ble/#
topic read hospital/medicine/command_ble_result/#

# Dashboard - read only access to everything
user dashboard
topic read hospital/#
